tika.dc.description:
Genealogists understand the value of a name and all the family history information names can provide. Now you can learn more about the Jewish names in your family tree with this comprehensive guide. Discover the meaning of popular Hebrew names.You'll also find:

  • Jewish naming patterns and traditions
  • Jewish emigration patterns
  • A pronunciation guide
